{"tid":868569,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登蝗語系列] 「支付」係唔係蝗語？","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T16:12:50.000Z","uid":1159,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae0192a362aa521965ce11f0a7979ccd6d039cd","tid":868569,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"Source: 香港公共圖書館香港舊報紙主題館藏<br />\n<a href=\"https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/web/guest/old-hk-collection?from_menu=Y&amp;dummy=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmis.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fweb%2Fguest%2Fold-hk-collection%3Ffrom_menu%3DY%26dummy%3D&d=BpnPxQCMLZFFl5rQmDXvreargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=c79e982f\" target=\"_blank\">https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/web/guest/old-hk-collection?from_menu=Y&amp;dummy=</a><br />\n<br />\n逢親有人用「支付」呢一個詞語，都會有人話應該用「付款」，「支付」一詞係蝗語。<br />\n<br />\n翻查香港公共圖書館香港舊報紙主題館藏，可見有紀錄「支付」一詞出現喺1854年嘅遐邇貫珍。而當時連中共甚至係民國都未成立。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IP77MoU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIP77MoU.jpg&h=e8da6e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>余共收捐項四百圓乃年中<strong>支付</strong>保項三百圓尚餘百圓為保主所得</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/X9gVYjG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FX9gVYjG.png&h=10f12a56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n縱觀分佈，「支付」一詞喺50-60年代更開始被廣泛使用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8Unpk29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8Unpk29.png&h=e7b38b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抽咗一份1952年嘅華僑日報，小標題同內文都有用「支付」一詞。<br />\n內文講述香港及日本之間應用何種貨幣支付<br />\n<br />\n咁睇下「付款」一詞，最早可見於1921年7月4日的香港華字日報<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XTVsOGx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXTVsOGx.png&h=248a1c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>中法實業銀行停止<strong>付款</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZU5I4NP.png?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZU5I4NP.png%3F1&h=d61d8a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再睇睇使用分佈，同「支付」一樣喺50-60年代廣泛使用，但係普及度似乎比「支付」為低<br />\n<br />\n所以由此可見，「支付」一詞不但<strong>並非蝗語</strong>，而且係「付款」有更長歷史的舊式中文。<br />\n<br />\n至於點解「支付」一詞會俾人以為係蝗語呢？<br />\n我個人估計應該近年支付寶嘅出現，喺品牌名稱使用咗「支付」呢個詞語。<br />\n翻查資料，支付寶喺2003年推出，近幾年先喺香港大事宣傳，再加上近年赤化問題嚴重，先會令人有咁嘅錯覺。"},{"pid":"6f737961aef61949e4bfab95029361c216a40b0e","tid":868569,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"摩牙? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93436daa3a7c4501f73895492f01c95844a4dc5","tid":868569,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f737961aef61949e4bfab95029361c216a40b0e","tid":868569,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"摩牙? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"其實呢個系列係另一位巴打做開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46778af00f749c5d9ed8e0268b2436f7e676ee8","tid":868569,"uid":192491,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"多謝班死支那人, 搞到明明係純正中文都變死蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ef43c17136c8d0506d2332650edfa1bf1a4edc","tid":868569,"uid":97451,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"add2010855f160fe53b1605505a2c941c0e874e5","tid":868569,"uid":91771,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"支付<br />\n支持<br />\n支那<br />\n惡臭你支<br />\n小支支<br />\n支那賤畜<br />\n他鄉遇故支<br />\n全部都唔係蝗語"},{"pid":"edb5063165db0bfebfaad8c74795e289c863d7ce","tid":868569,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除